channel.title: V2scape [634] - very complete - final release - no antileech
channel.description:
Server: ***
[b]Features:[/b] - All skills working - Jad (100%) (All waves) - Nex (100%) - Godwars (100%) - Duel Arena (100%) - Just about every mini-game completed. - Summoning (100%) - Full-screen - 634 character models - 634 items - 634 animations - 634 gfx - 508 maps - XP counter - 562 gameframe - New HP bars and fading hitmarks - Sprite outlining - Curses - 602 skilltab with hovers - 9 different crowns, one for each playerRights - Lots of model fixes have been applied - Items kept on death interface fully working - New bank interface with working deposit buttons - New shop interface - Some interface snippets have been added, the starters interface for example - New text engine implemented - Improved game engine A LOT
[b][u]A couple screenies (more coming):[/u][/b] [b]New interfaces[/b] [img]http://img152.imageshack.us/img152/8875/pk4.png[/img]
[b]Ganodermic[/b] [img]http://s16.postimg.org/l54mw85cl/Naamloos.png[/img]
Server: ***
Credits: Me Kemp (game engine) Sanity (source)
